#. <section class="sutta" id="sn4.11"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn4.11:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: 2. Dutiyavagga → rajjavaggo (bj) | rajjavaggo dutiyo (pts2)
msgctxt "sn4.11:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. Rule"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn4.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Pāsāṇasutta"
msgstr "11. Boulders"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.244"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.11:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati gijjhakūṭe pabbate."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, on the Vulture’s Peak "
"Mountain."

msgctxt "sn4.11:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā rattandhakāratimisāyaṃ abbhokāse nisinno "
"hoti, devo ca ekamekaṃ phusāyati."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time the Buddha was meditating in the open during the dark of "
"night, while a gentle rain drizzled down."

msgctxt "sn4.11:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho māro pāpimā bhagavato bhayaṃ chambhitattaṃ lomahaṃsaṃ uppādetukāmo "
"yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavato avidūre mahante pāsāṇe "
"padālesi."
msgstr ""
"Then Māra the Wicked, wanting to make the Buddha feel fear, terror, and "
"goosebumps, approached him, and crushed some large boulders close by him."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.11:2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā “māro ayaṃ pāpimā” iti viditvā māraṃ pāpimantaṃ gāthāya "
"ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha, knowing that this was Māra the Wicked, addressed him in "
"verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.11:3.1"
msgid "“Sacepi kevalaṃ sabbaṃ,"
msgstr "“Even if you shake"

#. <br>
#. VAR: calessasi → caleyyāsi (bj, mr) | gaḷeyyasi (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn4.11:3.2"
msgid "gijjhakūṭaṃ calessasi;"
msgstr "this entire Vulture’s Peak,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.11:3.3"
msgid "Neva sammāvimuttānaṃ,"
msgstr "the rightly released,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.11:3.4"
msgid "buddhānaṃ atthi iñjitan”ti."
msgstr "the awakened, are unshaken.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.11:4.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho māro pāpimā “jānāti maṃ bhagavā, jānāti maṃ sugato”ti dukkhī "
"dummano tatthevantaradhāyīti."
msgstr ""
"Then Māra the Wicked, thinking, “The Buddha knows me! The Holy One knows me!”"
" miserable and sad, vanished right there."
